Why Fraud Detection Matters in Parametric Insurance
Parametric insurance is powerful precisely because it's automated — but that same automation creates fraud surfaces. Without validation, bad actors could:

Fake GPS location to appear in a disrupted zone
File claims without ever being active on the platform
Create multiple accounts to multiply payouts for the same event

GigShield's 3-Layer Fraud Shield closes these gaps while keeping legitimate claims fast.

